0) Prerequisites (one-time)

Install Git: [git-scm.com] â†’ install, keep defaults.

Install VS Code: [code.visualstudio.com].

Tell Git who you are (once):

Open VS Code â†’ Terminal â†’ New Terminal and run:

git config --global user.name "Your Name"
